and wish you happy holidays.

97
00:05:03,074 --> 00:05:05,057
No, no, Mom and Herb
are out to dinner.

98
00:05:05,059 --> 00:05:07,827
I'm just chilling
at the ski lodge.

99
00:05:07,829 --> 00:05:09,495
Room service.

100
00:05:09,497 --> 00:05:10,613
Oh, hang on.

101
00:05:10,615 --> 00:05:11,664
I ordered
a cheeseburger.

102
00:05:11,666 --> 00:05:12,865
Got to go, Dad.

103
00:05:12,867 --> 00:05:14,667
Yeah, I know
the tip's included.

104
00:05:14,669 --> 00:05:16,452
All right, bye.

105
00:05:16,454 --> 00:05:17,453
All right, now you call your mom

106
00:05:17,455 --> 00:05:19,372
and tell her
you're with your dad.

107
00:05:22,709 --> 00:05:26,578
Hey, Mom, I'm with your dad.

108
00:05:26,580 --> 00:05:27,680
No, no.

109
00:05:29,466 --> 00:05:31,517
